Text: The keygen has a virus. I deleted from my computer right away!
Its a false positive....no one else has had problems

Downloaded again. Received Security Alert from Virus Protector -**** keygen.exe containing the virus or unwanted program ‘TR/Agent.16896.184 was blocked’****. Thanks anyways, but not worth the risk. Not sure what it will do because my virus protector detected this. Removed from computer. Better safe than sorry.
